@@ -0,0 +1,34 @@
+# PR 214 Review Reply Draft
+
+## T-214-01
+
+Addressed in `src/policy/preview.py:1-22` and `src/policy/approval_router.py:11-23`.
+The fallback payload now preserves `approval_state` and
+`requires_human_review`, and the router normalizes `manual_review` before
+building either preview shape. Verified with the preview-disabled regression
+case in `tests/test_preview.py:31-40`.
+
+## T-214-02
+
+Marked duplicate of `T-214-01`. The same reopened fallback regression was fixed
+once in `src/policy/preview.py:16-22`, so there is no separate code path to
+change here.
+
+## T-214-03
+
+Marked obsolete. The review export flags this thread as outdated, and reviving a
+legacy preview branch on the current diff would reintroduce a path we were asked
+not to restore.
+
+## T-214-04
+
+Addressed in `tests/test_preview.py:31-40`. Added a regression that exercises
+`build_policy_preview(..., approval_state="manual_review", preview_enabled=False, ...)`
+and asserts the fallback payload stays normalized to
+`human_review_required` with `requires_human_review == True`.
+
